\begin_layout Standard
There are various reasons why people run; some people do it to stay healthy,
 others do it for the competition.
 However, a large part of the population seems to struggle finding motivation
 to run or to exercise at all for that matter.
 A way to motivate people could be to make running more entertaining by
 adding game elements.
 
\end_layout

