\begin_layout Standard
Another application, called 
\emph on
Zombies, Run! 
\emph default

\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "SixtoStart2014"

\end_inset

, launched in 2012 focuses more on a fun game experience than on running
 statistics.
 The game elements provides an illusion of zombies chasing the user.
 This is done by generating the sound of zombies (a type of monsters) approachin
g the user.
 The sound only disappears if the user runs fast enough over a period of
 time, thus evading the zombies.
 Since the zombies has no location and thereby no direction relative to
 the user, the escape can be done in any direction.
\end_layout

